<div data-controller="appear">
  <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-12);">
    <h1 class="type-serif-display animate-fade-in-up">Our Story</h1>
    <p class="animate-fade-in-up delay-2" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); font-size: var(--text-lg); font-style: italic; margin-top: var(--space-4);">
      How two lives became one
    </p>
    <div class="divider divider-colored animate-fade-in delay-4">est. 2020</div>
  </div>

  <%# Chapter 1 — How We Met %>
  <div class="appear appear-delay-1" style="display: flex; gap: var(--space-4); align-items: stretch; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: var(--space-8);">
    <div class="photo-card" style="flex: 0 0 42%; min-height: 320px; border-radius: var(--radius-lg); overflow: hidden;">
      <%# Replace with: image_tag "story/how-we-met.jpg" %>
      <%= image_tag "events/venue1.jpg",
            style: "width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;",
            alt: "How We Met" %>
    </div>
    <section class="card" style="flex: 1; min-width: 260px; background: var(--color-celadon-bg); border-color: rgba(168, 198, 159, 0.4);">
      <div class="card-body">
        <p class="type-serif-small" style="color: var(--color-success); margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">Chapter One</p>
        <h2 class="card-title" style="font-size: var(--text-2xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">How We Met</h2>
        <p class="type-serif-body">
          Every love story has a beginning. Ours started with a chance encounter that neither of us expected — and neither of us could forget. What began as a simple introduction blossomed into something neither of us could have planned.
        </p>
        <p class="type-serif-body" style="margin-top: var(--space-4);">
          <%# Add your story here %>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <%# Chapter 2 — The Proposal %>
  <div class="appear appear-delay-2" style="display: flex; gap: var(--space-4); align-items: stretch; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: var(--space-8);">
    <section class="card" style="flex: 1; min-width: 260px; background: rgba(92, 93, 141, 0.06); border-color: rgba(92, 93, 141, 0.25);">
      <div class="card-body">
        <p class="type-serif-small" style="color: var(--color-accent); margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">Chapter Two</p>
        <h2 class="card-title" style="font-size: var(--text-2xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">The Proposal</h2>
        <p class="type-serif-body">
          When Gulbir got down on one knee, Nuvdeep knew this was the moment everything changed. Surrounded by the people and places they love most, he asked the question that would set the rest of their lives in motion.
        </p>
        <p class="type-serif-body" style="margin-top: var(--space-4);">
          <%# Add your proposal story here %>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <div class="photo-card" style="flex: 0 0 42%; min-height: 320px; border-radius: var(--radius-lg); overflow: hidden;">
      <%# Replace with: image_tag "story/proposal.jpg" %>
      <%= image_tag "events/venue2.jpg",
            style: "width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;",
            alt: "The Proposal" %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# Chapter 3 — Our Journey %>
  <div class="appear appear-delay-3" style="display: flex; gap: var(--space-4); align-items: stretch; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: var(--space-8);">
    <div class="photo-card" style="flex: 0 0 42%; min-height: 320px; border-radius: var(--radius-lg); overflow: hidden;">
      <%# Replace with: image_tag "story/engagement.jpg" %>
      <%= image_tag "events/venue5.jpg",
            style: "width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;",
            alt: "Our Journey" %>
    </div>
    <section class="card" style="flex: 1; min-width: 260px; background: rgba(101, 79, 111, 0.06); border-color: rgba(101, 79, 111, 0.2);">
      <div class="card-body">
        <p class="type-serif-small" style="color: var(--color-text-secondary); margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">Chapter Three</p>
        <h2 class="card-title" style="font-size: var(--text-2xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">Our Journey</h2>
        <p class="type-serif-body">
          From that first hello to planning a lifetime together — our journey has been filled with laughter, adventure, and the certainty that we were made for each other. And now, surrounded by everyone we love, we can't wait for the next chapter.
        </p>
        <p class="type-serif-body" style="margin-top: var(--space-4);">
          <%# Add your engagement story here %>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <%# Closing quote %>
  <div class="appear appear-delay-4 text-center" style="margin-top: var(--space-12); padding: var(--space-12) var(--space-8); background: var(--color-celadon-bg); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); border: 1px solid rgba(168, 198, 159, 0.4);">
    <p style="font-family: var(--font-script); font-size: var(--text-4xl); color: var(--color-text-secondary); line-height: 1.3;">
      And so the adventure begins...
    </p>
    <p class="type-serif-small" style="color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-top: var(--space-6);">
      NOVEMBER 25–28, 2026 &nbsp;&bull;&nbsp; ANAHEIM, CALIFORNIA
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
